![Smarteefi NS11 16A retrofit Node STD](https://i.imgur.com/EsM6iGw.jpg)

- It is possible to make a backup copy of the stock firmware with esptool.py
- Soldering a small wire to the GPIO 0 which is easily accessible next to the switch connector ensures easy flash mode by shorting to ground
- power the module from 3.3v only. DO NOT CONNECT TO MAINS WHEN FLASHING / WORKING on the board
- can use Webserial to flash tasmota 
- Requires power calibration after setup

## GPIO details

- GPIO 4 connection to external switch, can reprogram for any other purpose
- GPIO 14 Relay
- GPIO 16 Green LED
- GPIO 0 BL0937 SEL
- GPIO 5 BL0937 CF
- GPIO 13 BL0937 CF1
